<title>NA NGAIHCHIATNAK HLAW TUAH CH337</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hi vawlei ngaih-chiatnak vialte kha hlaw tuah, Zanlei caan tikah khan,
 Duhsah kan ruah lai Khuamui chungah chim tuah, Biatak in vaa pe, Jesuh
 sinah hal tuah, Thachin an pek lai.

[V2]
 Jesuh sinah chim tuah, Ngaih-chiatnak a hngalh, Jesuh na chimh ahcun,
 Thachin an pek lai. Na lam kha a ceu cang, Va kal law, khawm tuah, Hal
 tuah, na ngaih-chiatnak, Na thil a zaang lai.

[V3]
 Ngaihchiat lungrawhnak he, Khuamui hmanhsehlaw, Nangmah nak sifakmi,
 Va bawm zungzal hna. Ngaih-chiatnak kha hlaw tuah, Thachin hmuh awkah,
 Midang zong hmuh awkah, Jesuh sin hal tuah.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
</song>